## ðŸš€ Deploying ControlCenter Service

### What `deploy.sh` does:
- Publishes the .NET project to `/publish`
- Copies `controlcenter.service` to `/etc/systemd/system/`
- Reloads systemd
- Enables the service (auto-start on boot)
- Restarts the service
- Shows current service status
- Optionally tails live logs

### To deploy:
```bash
cd ControlCenter/ControlCenter
chmod +x scripts/deploy.sh
./scripts/deploy.sh
